{"tid":1428121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭冇份返大陸開會","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:49.000Z","uid":203010,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99cbf6e2fd1f5b83239bbd50513f5d048d850e12","tid":1428121,"uid":203010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"by pass林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473241-20190807.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473241-20190807.htm&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=a5c59736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473241-20190807.htm&h=0c600ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473241-20190807.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，張曉明認為，現階段成立獨立調查委員會並不合適，現時最重要止暴制亂，否則社會不能運行，組織調查也沒有意思。目前社會賢達組成的監警會，相信處理投訴警察個案時不會偏頗，但在事件平息後則可以考慮成立獨立調查委員會，至於出動駐港解放軍方面，消息指，張曉明沒有提及期限，亦沒有提到特區政府班子需要調整。"}]}